usb: typec: clean up RTS5453 ACPI USB-DP integration for 6.18

Keep the permanent CIX ACPI USB-DP integration separate from generic Type-C lookup helpers on 6.18: defer until USB-DP providers exist, keep role-switch optional under PNP0D10, share IRQs deterministically, and harden USB-DP child fwnode lookup.

